{"type": "article", "id": 3067, "title": "防止标签滑入的茶包", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-27T08:05:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233020bzMg8Jq2cFfB3KpY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t世界上许多国家都有茶文化，散茶是常态，但自 20 世纪初以来，袋泡茶逐渐流行起来。不过大多数茶客都会被一个问题所困扰，那就是袋泡茶的标签容易落入杯子的不便。日前，来自台湾的设计师 Tseng Yiwen 想出了一个简单的解决办法，为袋泡茶的标签涂抹上类似于邮票粘合剂的东西，泡茶时，水汽蒸腾，变得湿润的标签条就会贴在杯子的外壁上，不会滑入杯子内部，这是一个非常低成本的解决方案，还收获了今年的<a href=\"http://www.red-dot.sg/en/online-exhibition/concept/?code=1366&amp;y=2014&amp;c=23&amp;a=0\" target=\"_blank\">德国红点奖</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233019hUGWRernAYVEDNL2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052330198cLgVrvHqEdoWwTY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052330203nSxp2rPHD1zkdLh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}